SCHOOL MANAGEMENT SYSTEM This system will monitor, record attendance of students and teachers and thus Lecturers are able to identify when a student is absent. The event tab identifies the subject, you can also create a user who can manipulate the recording of every student. This system was proudly created by a team's effort of Fred Gichohi, Kevin Kinyua, Cynthia Pendo, Nigel Owiti, Joey Shem and Innocent Mambo. This system was created using Micrrosoft Visual Studio 2019 and supported by use of Microsoft Access 2019.
Proudly Kenyan. #ByKenyans for Kenyans
